quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,59,"Ampa sε, Yε’somaa Noah kͻͻ ne nkorͻfoͻ hͻ. Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, monsom Nyankopͻn, na monni awurade foforͻ biara wͻ N’akyi. Nokorε sε mesuro Da kεseε no asotwee no ma mo “"
  7,60,"Nhemfo a εwͻ nenkorͻfoͻ no mu no kaa sε: “Yehu wo sε wo wͻ ͻyera pefee paa mu “"
  7,61,"Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, εnyε yera na mayera, na mmom meyε Ɔsomafoͻ firi Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ"
  7,62,"Me Wura Nyankopͻn Asεm no ho dawuro na merebɔ akyerε mo, na merema mo afutupa, na menim adeε a monnim wͻ Nyankopͻn hͻ"
  7,63,Anaasε εyε mo nwanwa sε Afutusεm fri mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ nam momu nipa bi so aba mo hͻ sεdeε ͻde bεbͻ mo kͻkͻ na mobεyε ahwεyie ama yahu mo mmͻbͻ
  7,64,"Nanso wͻ’buu no nkontomponi, enti Yε’gyee no, ne wͻn a wͻ’ka ne ho no wͻ εhyεn no mu no nkwa, na Yε’maa nsuo faa wͻn a wͻ’faa Yεn Nsεm no atorͻsεm no. Nokorε sε, na wͻ’yε nnipa a wͻn ani afira"